# Portfolio Project Rules

## Stack

- Vanilla HTML/CSS, Vite 5 build, Biome 2.3+ lint/format, Node 24 (via mise)
- Single CSS file: `assets/jeffrey.css` (component styles) — never hand-create CSS files. Design tokens live in `tokens/*.tokens.json` → generated `assets/tokens.generated.css` (`npm run tokens`); see `design/DESIGN_SPEC.md`
- Minimal JS: only `assets/menu.js` for mobile nav — ask before adding any script

## Key commands

```bash
mise run ci        # lint + format-check + build (run before done)
mise run dev       # dev server at localhost:5173
mise run build     # production build to dist/
mise run lint:fix  # lint + auto-fix
mise run format    # format with Biome
```

## Hard boundaries

**Never:**
- Add external font loading, tracking scripts, or heavy dependencies
- Break existing page URLs (may be bookmarked or externally linked)
- Disable Biome rules to silence errors
- Write to `node_modules/`, `dist/`, or `package-lock.json`
- Add `<style>` blocks or inline styles — everything goes in `assets/jeffrey.css`

**Ask first:**
- New npm dependencies
- New HTML entry points (also requires `vite.config.js` entry in rollupOptions.input)
- Changes to the design system (colors, typography, spacing scale)
- Changes to `.github/workflows/deploy.yml`
- Structural changes affecting navigation or the site map

## Design system quick reference

- **Spacing**: `--space-1` through `--space-5` (rem-based — never arbitrary px values)
- **Colors**: `--ink` (text), `--paper` (bg), `--muted` (secondary), `--accent` (blue links), `--accent-2` (green)
- **Typography**: `--font` (system sans-serif), `--mono` (monospace) — no web fonts
- **Layout**: `--measure` (72ch max-width), 768px mobile breakpoint
- **Shape**: `--radius` (14px), `--radius-sm` (10px), `--border`, `--shadow`, `--shadow-hard`

## Page structure

Every page: `<header>` → `<main>` → `<footer>`
Heading hierarchy must be continuous — never skip levels.

## Triage map

- Styles → `assets/jeffrey.css`
- Mobile nav → `assets/menu.js`
- Build inputs → `vite.config.js` rollupOptions.input
- CI/CD → `.github/workflows/deploy.yml`
- Lint/format config → `biome.json`
- Project pages → `projects/*.html`
- Safe sandbox (not deployed) → `experiments/`
